reviewText: Great condition no problem with it thanks again for letting me purchasing the movies. Finding them both together is a tough find
The original Van Wilder is totally hilarious...and VERY off color!  Guess that's what makes it fun.

Van Wilder is one of those films that I rarely admit to enjoying. Although its humor could be considered juvenile, I don't care. It is disgusting in some areas, but I enjoy Ryan Reynolds so much that I don't care. Don't expect rocket science, but enjoy this for what it is: silly, dirty fun.
Had to introduce my GF to this classic that was before her time. Second one was terrible.
Great movie, dvd came in perfect shape!
Very funny and good to have both movies.
